Jay Sheffield https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jay_Sheffield 0 Jay Howard Sheffield (September 25, 1934 - June 25, 1998) was an American actor, who appeared in the film The Three Stooges Go Around the World in a Daze. Sheffield played Phileas Fogg III, the great grandson of Phileas Fogg. He appeared as a guest star in many television shows, including on six episodes of Hogan's Heroes.
